<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>IS YOUR ALL ON THE ALTAR?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Muonna kim na deih a, ginna hat na nawp leh,
 Aw, na lungthim chengin na ngenin;
 Mahleh chawlhdamna leh kipahna mu puon la,
 Na bangkim Amah na piek macheng.

[V2]
 Aw, na bangkim Lalpa kawmah na pie tam?
 Thagau in a hun pui thei nam?
 Na sapum, na thagau, na bangkim na piek chun,
 Kipahna, chawlhdamna nei inla.

[V3]
 2. Kipak leh lungdam in Lalpa tawh kitawn in,
 Amah thu vaka chieh na nuom em?
 A deih bang thil bawlin gitlohna thihsan in,
 Na bangkim Amah kawmah pie'n la.

[V4]
 3. Aw, I he thei ngei puou, Lalpa'n ei piek thilte,
 Vangsakna A kawma nget ding le;
 I sapum, I thagau Ama'n A neih ma cheng,
 I bangkim Amah I piek macheng.

[V5]
 4. Hehpihna ei piekin ei kipahsak intin,
 Kuoman genthei in, gen seng, lo ding;
 I bangkim pie leu hing Aman ei umpih ding,
 Kipahna, chawlhdamna mu tai tiu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>324</hymn_number>
</song>